data.description: Check out this refreshed home in convenient Carriage Pointe South! This 2018 build is Move-in ready with new interior paint and new carpet in the bedrooms. Situated at the end of street with no direct side or rear neighbors. Open floorplan with spacious kitchen overlooking the great room and dining room. Kitchen features espresso wood cabinets, granite countertops, bar seating and large pantry. Dining space leads to the covered patio and private backyard. Primary suite is separated from the secondary bedrooms. Complete with walk-in closet, dual sink and enclosed water closet, you are sure to appreciate this private retreat. Great location gives you easy access to I-75, Hwy 301 and Hwy 41. Close to tons of shopping, movie theatre and restaurants as well. Carriage Pointe South features a clubhouse, pool, playground, fitness center, basketball and tennis court. All of these amenities are easily accessible using the endless sidewalks found throughout the community allowing you to enjoy biking, dog-walking, and jogging all year round! Come see this home today and make it yours!
